    "description": "Evening plan integrating Madison Square Park stroll and a nearby dinner plan (restaurant choice + how to reserve)"
  },
  {
    "outcome_id": "outcome_4",
    "description": "Mobility and energy disclaimers/guide integrated into the itinerary (before-you-go notes and inline cautions)"
  }
]

List intentions and assign each outcome to one. JSON only.

